snippet.title: 'Aquaman' Producer Responds To Johnny Depp Fans Pushing For Amber Heard's Firing From Sequel
snippet.description:
"Aquaman" producer Peter Safran shuts down fan pressure to fire Amber Heard for the upcoming sequel, "Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom" and tells Deadline, "You gotta do what’s best for the movie."
